#META# contentSummary: A brief note sent by Muḥammad b. ʿAlī to Muʿtamid al-Mulk Abū Bakr, asking the latter to pay 30 *mann *of grain to a certain friend. The sender also asks the recipient to issue a note of note of delivery (*taslīm*), since he wrote a proof document, indicating that the friend may collect the debt whenever he wished.
